<div class="dablink">This article is about the Hindu god of creation.  For the Buddhist concept, see <a href="/wiki/Brahma_(Buddhism)" title="Brahma (Buddhism)" class="mw-redirect">Brahma (Buddhism)</a>. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Brahman_(disambiguation)" title="Brahman (disambiguation)">Brahman (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
